    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed manual transmission. This driver-focused example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS service to ensure peak valvetrain timing. The factory M-variable differential lock provides exceptional traction out of corners, while the suspension geometry remains true for precise turn-in. An honest, mechanically robust unit with no modifications to the drivetrain, offering the tactile feedback and linear power delivery sought by purists.",
      "price": 34500.0,
