    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between high-end performance and daily sophistication. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish that has been regularly detailed, showing only the lightest signs of careful road use consistent with a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any significant wear, while the dashboard and wood trim components retain their original factory sheen. Every electronic feature, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control and heated seats, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, having adhered to a strict schedule of preventative maintenance. The engine runs smoothly and quietly, paired with a transmission that provides crisp, precise shifts. Recent service includes a fresh oil change, new brake pads, and a multi-point inspection to ensure it is road-trip ready. With a clean title and a smoke-free interior, this vehicle offers a premium driving experience for the discerning buyer who values both style and substance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
