    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable set of wheels without any fuss. It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so you can just hop in and go! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin. I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home!",
