    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving pinnacle, powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double VANOS system for optimized cam phasing. The drivetrain is paired with a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, providing exceptional tactile feedback and power delivery. This chassis has been proactively maintained with documented subframe reinforcement and recent rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural integrity under high-G cornering. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, offering a communicative and balanced handling profile. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with a clean oil analysis history, making it an ideal candidate for the purist driver.",
